{"tid":688882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【生態危機】痛心內地人偷捕彈塗魚 觀鳥人士：你捉晒咁啲雀食乜？","createTime":"2018-06-03T15:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T11:56:04.000Z","uid":160628,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0a34831290097a1994ec129310a59a1d80838494","tid":688882,"uid":160628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"內地漁民擅闖米埔偷捕彈塗魚的情況，近日疑因電視節目推介下令彈塗魚身價上升，而變本加厲，他們日光日白公然在米埔泥灘上放置竹籠，將俗稱「花魚」的彈塗魚和其他泥灘生物趕盡殺絕，令環保人士擔心彈塗魚數量減少，影響生態。有觀鳥人士今早表示，對內地漁民的行為感到憤怒又痛心，但明白警方執法有一定困難，建議政府可與內地執法部門加強合作打擊。<br />\n<br />\n觀鳥人士李先生指出，內地漁民偷捕彈塗魚「不嬲都有，佢哋喺米埔浮橋嗰邊，我冇禁區紙入唔到去，唔係新鮮事，年年都有」，但擔心有電視節目推介彈塗魚後，令情況惡化，「梗係唔好啦，你捉晒，啲雀食乜呢」。李先生稱，經常見到內地漁民在米埔浮橋出沒，但觀鳥人士要進入浮橋，要向警方申請禁區紙，一般情況下「我地最多入到基圍」。　<br />\n<br />\n李先生不滿說：「大陸佬，乜鬼都話補，乜鬼都話壯陽，彈塗魚成日喺泥捐嚟捐去，應該一陣泥味，唔方好食！」他認為有更多食物可以取代彈塗魚，無必要為此破壞環境。李先生又指，明白警方難於執法，「你去捉佢時，佢（漁民）即刻走番大陸」，但認為政府「都要做啲嘢」，如可與內地執法部門加強溝通，合作打擊偷捕彈塗魚的情況。<br />\n<br />\n文章來源：<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180603/58271728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180603%2F58271728&d=hpq7ZA7EHjIIdPpRstEu%2FE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=f2fd5f8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180603%2F58271728&h=52637578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180603/58271728</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴撚線 乜撚都放入口 仲要捉到嚟香港 點捉翻大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0080d9a8e74563417806b1eff1cdc5a2951c794","tid":688882,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"捉埋d雀食囉"},{"pid":"b4614e9f8f147298c6b62c25aa71cc2b4c3dd75c","tid":688882,"uid":108631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0080d9a8e74563417806b1eff1cdc5a2951c794","tid":688882,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"捉埋d雀食囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4363fb88412cec49f8dc809223b059b0e1190b","tid":688882,"uid":108631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"大陸人究竟有咩係唔捉 有咩係唔會破壞 痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd5f0457658157bcac9b105ffc9955686ebda97","tid":688882,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e4363fb88412cec49f8dc809223b059b0e1190b","tid":688882,"uid":108631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"大陸人究竟有咩係唔捉 有咩係唔會破壞 痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:15:02.000Z","msg":"仲有中國人究竟有幾虧 下下都要壯陽"},{"pid":"bd7d1e23955d22ba11d48e1c6f69f3dc7109ab35","tid":688882,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:16:20.000Z","msg":"香港人冇得救<br />\n俾人恰到咁仲可以愛與和平感化人"},{"pid":"cb57d2f10d2719ecfea958fb37fe209686cef96c","tid":688882,"uid":44858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:21:26.000Z","msg":"大陸佬，乜鬼都話補，乜鬼都話壯陽<br />\n<br />\n人地虧麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3f4ae7708a9119fca87f8efee95d7757df79f8","tid":688882,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蝗禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef8af72f76a83b095e30f9392d6a885db1c38fe","tid":688882,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:30:45.000Z","msg":"彈塗魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decdf92e1e7007363c24d37707acb53e0a26483f","tid":688882,"uid":37413,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:31:13.000Z","msg":"大陸豬係唔會理你啲雀食乜，呢個係極度賤格自撚私畜生民族，佢話之啲雀絕種都不屑一顧，只會在乎自己口腔快感"},{"pid":"090b82f1a55c078e154fb55e6076306f884ee868","tid":688882,"uid":168525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"decdf92e1e7007363c24d37707acb53e0a26483f","tid":688882,"uid":37413,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:31:13.000Z","msg":"大陸豬係唔會理你啲雀食乜，呢個係極度賤格自撚私畜生民族，佢話之啲雀絕種都不屑一顧，只會在乎自己口腔快感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:38:25.000Z","msg":"大陸人只會覺得d雀同佢地爭魚食<br />\n要捉埋d雀黎食"},{"pid":"c950bdfa9bedccbcdd757ef078a02e1cacb93623","tid":688882,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:40:42.000Z","msg":"香港人：你地住晒咁香港人住邊？"},{"pid":"886955e74fb425974d0d7ce0b9da590d60e9c6b9","tid":688882,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T00:42:52.000Z","msg":"中國人：沒事兒，鳥也吃了不就沒問題嗎"},{"pid":"76d5071a364087d17b4514f8d2798c2a4e2f1400","tid":688882,"uid":178876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"d偷捕賊畀人點晒相<br />\n會唔會畀人用氣槍射架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人身安全令人擔心"}]}